column5: Centrally located 2nd floor garage apt w private entrance. 1 bd and private bathroom. Queen size bed with Tempur-Pedic mattress. 2 twin size air mattresses and a sofa to sleep on. Full size kitchen with dishwasher, oven, 5 burners, large fridge and microwave. Smart TV in living room and a TV in the bedroom. Full size washer and dryer. 1 off street covered parking space and 1 other uncovered off street space. Walking distance to many restaurants, cafes, and neighborhood bars. Close to bus routes.
